  <summary>Make games, animations, and stories</summary>
  <description>
    <p>A mod of TurboWarp (MistWarp) with live collaboration, total Chinese translations, and more.</p>
    <p>You can also use Bilup in your browser at https://editor.bilup.org/editor</p>
  </description>
  <url type="homepage">https://www.bilup.org/</url>
  <url type="bugtracker">https://github.com/Bilup/desktop/issues</url>
  <url type="translate">https://docs.bilup.org/translate</url>
